Package test

Class Testcase

java.lang.Object
test.Testcase
public class Testcase extends Object
This is used for testing classes in Testbed, represents a specific testcase for the class being tested, with the really generic use of Object, can cause errors if casted wrong
Author:
Michael Liu, Genfu Liu
